  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Our Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-[Archive] function and [Achievement] system are now live!-</strong></h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054150/extras/b106b9e7d7274cf3b8d47212412f4a30.poster.avif?t=1733127865\" width=606 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054150/extras/b106b9e7d7274cf3b8d47212412f4a30.webm?t=1733127865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054150/extras/b106b9e7d7274cf3b8d47212412f4a30.mp4?t=1733127865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054150/extras/fb06af5f1e4bf590859ab78e9d26b566.webp?t=1733127865\" width=607 height=55 /></span><br><br>Brave Player, fight and defend your towers! TOWER DEFENDER is a strategy TD game. Make deployment routes, release supernatural spells, conquer enemy towers and obtain victory. Defeat Dragon Boss and restore world peace!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054150/extras/d1af83ba234cb73cd423328d856b32a0.poster.avif?t=1733127865\" width=606 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054150/extras/d1af83ba234cb73cd423328d856b32a0.webm?t=1733127865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054150/extras/d1af83ba234cb73cd423328d856b32a0.mp4?t=1733127865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054150/extras/e021f8b9c44af4a2f4c1395f2d664a41.webp?t=1733127865\" width=607 height=55 /></span><br><br>500 years ago, five Guardians worked together to seal the evil dragon on the lava island. 500 years later, the dragon gradually woke up, and the world once again fell into crisis.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054150/extras/5310a51f112b9c828bbcd0e27e98e465.poster.avif?t=1733127865\" width=606 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054150/extras/5310a51f112b9c828bbcd0e27e98e465.webm?t=1733127865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054150/extras/5310a51f112b9c828bbcd0e27e98e465.mp4?t=1733127865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You, as the Commander of the Silver Knights, are endowed with the spells and skills of the Guardians. You can break through the casual mode to practice your skills, or you can challenge the dragon boss and fight to the death!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054150/extras/04d77299db88955a7e239600290fa954.webp?t=1733127865\" width=607 height=55 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Added [Archive function], now you can freely archive the game progress<br></li><li>Added [Achievement System], unlock the level to get surprise rewards<br></li><li>Become a kingdom warrior, strategically attack towers, defeat the boss, and restore world peace<br></li><li>Multiple gameplay modes: Survival and Casual<br></li><li>Experience the changing scenes: Forest, Snowland, Desert, and Cemetry<br></li><li>Battle Experience: Your soldiers and towers will gradually become more powerful as you defeat more enemies and complete more levels<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054150/extras/652a5a270e5a05a38588d4b74771c544.poster.avif?t=1733127865\" width=606 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054150/extras/652a5a270e5a05a38588d4b74771c544.webm?t=1733127865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054150/extras/652a5a270e5a05a38588d4b74771c544.mp4?t=1733127865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
